      {
        "text": "### Select Your Data\n- Click the empty cell in the upper-left of your dataset\n- This will select all rows and columns",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/c802ab890b90ef23a9b2766f3aadddaa-L7P5-1_2.gif",
        "key": "hardware-components-3d887b32-d501-4032-b990-2a51ae5b4de8",
        "layout": "text-bottom-right",
        "typing": false,
        "fadeInOverPrevious": false
      },
      {
        "text": "### Open the Sorting Menu\n- Click **Data** > **Sort Range**\n- Select **Advanced range sorting options**",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/35deb5e7acd943d4f80686379b6414a1-L7P5-2_2-ezgif.com-optimize.gif",
        "key": "data-science-lesson7-panel5-2025-launch-109d0466-9ca3-4cc7-86b0-0af49c80e409",
        "layout": "text-bottom-left"
      },
      {
        "text": "### Sort the Data\n- Select \"**Data has header row**\"\n- Select a *column* within **Sort by...**\n- Choose the *direction* to sort (**A-Z** or **Z-A**)\n- Click **Sort**",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/edfd140e982759a482b7c50e881b0322-L7P5-3_5-ezgif.com-optimize.gif",
